LCS/Common package
==================

The LCS/Common package contains pieces of software that are very
reusable. Hence the name "common".

Although being one package, one can identify a number of groups, each group
providing distinct functionality:

  * Blitz++ to AIPS++ conversion functions
      Conversion methods for Blitz++ and AIPS++ data structures.
  * Blob Binary Large Objects (Blob)
      Classes for serializing one or more objects into a blob and
      de-serializingthe blob to objects.
  * Data conversion functions
  * Logging package
  * Profiling MPI Profiling
  * Sockets
  * Shared Memory
  * Threads
  * Type name functions
